<task id="task-4256" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">In manual view</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Open a test case in the&#160; <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-manual" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> &#160;view. Click on the drop-down icon of the <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-add" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> button, then choose <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-looping-statements" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>. </cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To add a keyword under a statement, select that statement, then click <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-add" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="600" href="../Images/830-for-while.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Looping statement</alt></image><p class="- topic/p ">Refer to the following table for the usage of each statement:</p><p class="- topic/p "><table class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry class="- topic/entry ">Statement</entry><entry class="- topic/entry ">Description</entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry class="- topic/entry ">For</entry><entry class="- topic/entry ">This statement accepts a range, list, or array as an input value so that Katalon Studio knows how many times to execute all steps within the&#160;<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">For</uicontrol>&#160;structure.</entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry class="- topic/entry ">While</entry><entry class="- topic/entry ">This statement requires a boolean condition as the input value so that <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> keeps executing all steps within until the condition fails.</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></p></info></step></steps></taskbody></task>